在俄罗斯的斡旋下，亚美尼亚、阿塞拜疆和[[阿尔察赫共和国|阿尔察赫共和国]]（非缔约国）于2020年11月9日达成[[2020年纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫停火协议|停火协议]]，莫斯科11月10日午夜起正式生效，解释纳卡地区的所有敌对需要都要结束<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ria.ru/20201110/karabakh-1583847112.html|title=Путин выступил с заявлением о прекращении огня в Карабахе|date=2020-11-09|access-date=2020-11-09|work=RIA Novosti|language=ru|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115170226/https://ria.ru/20201110/karabakh-1583847112.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://ria.ru/20201110/karabakh-1583845291.html|title=Пашинян заявил о прекращении боевых действий в Карабахе|date=2020-11-09|access-date=2020-11-09|work=RIA Novosti|language=ru|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115170154/https://ria.ru/20201110/karabakh-1583845291.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ria.ru/20201110/karabakh-1583847338.html|title=Президент непризнанной НКР дал согласие закончить войну|date=2020-11-09|access-date=2020-11-09|work=RIA Novosti|language=ru|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115170204/https://ria.ru/20201110/karabakh-1583847338.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿塞拜疆控制了5个城市、4座城镇和240个村庄外加整个[[阿塞拜疆–伊朗边境|阿塞拜疆–伊朗边境]]，宣布获得胜利<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnnturk.com/dunya/son-dakika-haberi-azerbaycan-cumhurbaskani-duyurdu-49-yerlesim-yeri-daha-kurtarildi|title=Son dakika haberi: Azerbaycan Cumhurbaşkanı duyurdu: 49 yerleşim yeri daha kurtarıldı|work=CNN Türk|date=2020-11-09|access-date=2020-11-09|language=tr|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115170214/https://www.cnnturk.com/dunya/son-dakika-haberi-azerbaycan-cumhurbaskani-duyurdu-49-yerlesim-yeri-daha-kurtarildi|dead-url=no}}</ref>。纳卡部分地区及[[亞美尼亞控制的納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫周邊地區|亞美尼亞控制的納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫周邊地區]]于2020年12月1日割让予阿塞拜疆，阿塞拜疆可以通过穿越亚美尼亚走廊，获得外飞地[[纳希切万自治共和国|纳希切万自治共和国]]的土地使用权，同样亚美尼亚也可以通过穿越阿塞拜疆的走廊获得纳希切万自治共和国的土地使用权<ref>{{cite web|last=Kramer|first=Andrew E.|date=2020-11-10|title=Facing Military Debacle, Armenia Accepts a Deal in Nagorno-Karabakh War|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/09/world/middleeast/armenia-settlement-nagorno-karabakh-azerbaijan.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111011541/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/09/world/middleeast/armenia-settlement-nagorno-karabakh-azerbaijan.html|archive-date=2020-11-11|issn=0362-4331}}</ref>。

在{{tsl|en|Rustam Muradov|鲁斯塔姆·穆拉多夫}}的带领下，约2000名俄罗斯士兵<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.turan.az/ext/news/2020/11/free/politics%20news/en/129784.htm|title=General Rustam Muradov is appointed Commander of Russian peacekeepers in Karabakh|date=2020-11-11|access-date=2020-11-11|work=Turan Information Agency|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115170154/https://www.turan.az/ext/news/2020/11/free/politics%20news/en/129784.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>以维护部队的身份进驻亚美尼亚和纳卡地区直接的陆路走廊进行保护，期限至少5年<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/11/09/armenian-pm-announces-end-to-nagorno-karabakh-hostilities-a71997|title=Deal Struck to End Nagorno-Karabakh War|work=The Moscow Times|access-date=2020-11-10|date=2020-11-10|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115170217/https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2020/11/10/russian-peacekeepers-head-to-nagorno-karabakh-after-peace-deal-a71997|dead-url=no}}</ref>。俄罗斯部队还将负责管理连接阿塞拜疆和纳希切万的陆路<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-54882564|title=Armenia, Azerbaijan and Russia sign Nagorno-Karabakh peace deal|date=2020-11-10|access-date=2020-11-10|work=BBC News|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115170225/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-54882564|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
===2021年衝突===
2021年11月中旬，阿塞拜疆與亞美尼亞再次爆發衝突。亚美尼亚军队共有1人死亡，13人被俘，另有24人失踪，两个阵地被佔領<ref>{{cite news |title=亚美尼亚国防部：与阿塞拜疆冲突中丢失两个阵地 |url=https://m.sohu.com/a/501550054_115479/?pvid=000115_3w_a |accessdate=2021-11-17 |archive-date=2021-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211117085204/https://m.sohu.com/a/501550054_115479/?pvid=000115_3w_a }}</ref>。阿塞拜疆军方在冲突中共有近70人伤亡。<ref>{{cite news |title=亚美尼亚国防部：与阿塞拜疆边境冲突中1人死亡24人失踪 |url=https://world.huanqiu.com/article/45cd7r4Itis |accessdate=2021-11-17 |archive-date=2021-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211122235545/https://world.huanqiu.com/article/45cd7r4Itis }}</ref>
